for i in range(10):
    print(f'''
    if df.loc[:, 'pnl{i}'].sum() < profit_target and df.loc[:, 'pnl{i}'].sum() > 0:
        if not in_position{i}: 
            side{i} = choice([-1, 1])
            entry = df.iloc[i].price
            tp{i} = entry + side{i} * profit_max
            sl{i} = entry - side{i} * loss_max 
            in_position{i} = True
        else:
            if (df.loc[:, 'price'].iloc[i] - tp{i}) * side{i} >= 0:
                df.loc[:, 'pnl{i}'].iloc[i] = profit_max
                in_position{i} = False
            if (df.loc[:, 'price'].iloc[i] - sl{i}) * side{i} <= 0:
                df.loc[:, 'pnl{i}'].iloc[i] = -loss_max
                in_position{i} = False
        if i == df.shape[0]-1:
            df.loc[:, 'pnl{i}'].iloc[i] = (df.loc[:, 'price'].iloc[i] - entry)* side{i}''')

    if df.loc[:, 'pnl0'].sum() < profit_target and df.loc[:, 'pnl0'].sum() > 0:
        if not in_position0: 
            side0 = choice([-1, 1])
            entry = df.iloc[i].price
            tp0 = entry + side0 * profit_max
            sl0 = entry - side0 * loss_max 
            in_position0 = True
        else:
            if (df.loc[:, 'price'].iloc[i] - tp0) * side0 >= 0:
                df.loc[:, 'pnl0'].iloc[i] = profit_max
                in_position0 = False
            if (df.loc[:, 'price'].iloc[i] - sl0) * side0 <= 0:
                df.loc[:, 'pnl0'].iloc[i] = -loss_max

            if (df.loc[:, 'price'].iloc[i] - tp99) * side99 >= 0:
                df.loc[:, 'pnl99'].iloc[i] = (df.loc[:, 'price'].iloc[i] - entry) * side99
                in_position99 = False
            if (df.loc[:, 'price'].iloc[i] - sl99) * side99 <= 0:
                df.loc[:, 'pnl99'].iloc[i] = (df.loc[:, 'price'].iloc[i] - entry) * side99
                in_position99 = False

        
        pnl_cum = pnl_cum + df.loc[:, 'pnl1'].iloc[i] 
        t.set_description(f"j={j} P/L = {pnl_cum}") 
        t.refresh()

    pt = pd.concat([
        df[['time','price']].reset_index().drop('index',axis=1), 
        df.reset_index().drop(['index','size','price', 'time'],axis=1).cumsum()
        ], axis=1)
    total = np.where(df.reset_index().drop(['index','size','price', 'time'],axis=1) !=0, 1, 0).sum().mean()/100
    wins = np.where(df.reset_index().drop(['index','size','price', 'time'],axis=1) >0, 1, 0).sum().mean()/100
    losts = np.where(df.reset_index().drop(['index','size','price', 'time'],axis=1) <0, 1, 0).sum().mean()/100
    avg_dd = -np.where(pt.reset_index().drop(['index','price', 'time'],axis=1) <0, 1, 0).mean()
    duration = (pt.time.max() - pt.time.min()).total_seconds()
    avg_pnl = round(pt.drop(['time', 'price'], axis=1).iloc[-1].mean(),0)
    median_pnl = round(pt.drop(['time', 'price'], axis=1).iloc[-1].median(),0)
    avg_std = round(pt.drop(['time', 'price'], axis=1).iloc[-1].std(),0)
    avg_pnl_net = (avg_pnl*20-total*2.15)/20
    avg_win_rate = round(wins/total*100,2)

    config = {
        'sim_id' : sim_id,
        'loss_max' : loss_max,
        'profit_max' : profit_max,
        'max_seconds_in_trade' : max_seconds_in_trade,
        'nb_total_trades': total,
        'nb_wins': wins,
        'nb_losts': losts,
        'avg_dd': avg_dd,
        'duration': duration,
        'avg_pnl': avg_pnl,
        'median_pnl': median_pnl,
        'avg_std': avg_std,
        'avg_pnl_net': avg_pnl_net,
        'avg_win_rate': avg_win_rate,
    }
    configs.append(config)

    df.to_parquet(f'data/simulations/full/NQ_trades_{sim_id}.parquet')

    fig = pt.plot(x='time', secondary_y='price',figsize=(16,8), legend=False, 
    title=f'''from {pt.time.min()}  to ->  {pt.time.max()}  -  Duration= {duration} seconds
    Avg P/L = {avg_pnl}  -  P/L net = {avg_pnl_net}  -  Median P/L = {median_pnl}  -  Std P/L = {avg_std}
    Avg # trades = {total}  -  Avg win rate = {avg_win_rate}%  -  Avg Drawdown= {avg_dd}
    ''').get_figure()
    fig.savefig(f'data/simulations/full/{sim_id}.png')

    with open('data/simulations/full/simu_configs.json', 'w') as f:
        f.write(pd.DataFrame(configs).T.to_json())
